N> Dial </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Corp. </ORGANIZATION>, reported net income of $ 14.7 million for the second quarter, up from $ 13.3 million a year earlier. The service group had earnings of $ 22.8 million, up from $ 15.3 million in the second quarter of 1987. The transportation-manufacturing group's profit rose to $ 7.8 million from $ 6 million a year earlier.
